{
  "stem": "18626.11",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But inside, in the-- in the place, in Dachau in the yard, all over, I could go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wasn't afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was all the time in the yard all kind of, believe me, securities or FBI or CIA, who knows what?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was all the time people around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, I was not, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I can name my people who I knew and what I was going to testify against them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And before I was going to testify, I was given orders and a law to obey.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the law and the order to obey was when I'm called on the stand and I'm called in to show and to recognize and to make sure that that's the prisoner I'm testifying against, I'm allowed to stay-- to go up on the stand, like a tribune, to him and stay away from him 12 inches.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[POINTING] With my finger away from him 12 inches, that's what I'm allowed to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I cannot do-- no closer go to him, or no violent moves to make on him, and to be restrained, and keep my temper at all time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was told that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But, to regret, it didn't turn out that way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was called to the stand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was, you, Morris-- you, Moses Rutschaisky, swear to God nothing but the truth to tell so-- God-- so help you God?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I do.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They start to ask me the questions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What did you see?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What happened when you came to Dachau?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I says, when I came to Dachau, we were taken off the trains.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And by the train was already the commandant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Where's the-- what's his name?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Johann Kirsch, he came to greet us by the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What happened then?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
